Salting foods

sel de guerande 86% chlorure de sodium
    0.25tsp = 1.3g 
        = 1.12g chlorure de sodium
        = 450mg sodium

sel = 40% sodium

= Sodium content of foods
- Beef : 88mg sodium/100g
- cheese : 660mg sodium/100g
- beurre Gaborit demi sel : 450mg/100g

= Potassium content of foods
- Beef : 365mg potassium/100g
- cheese : negligeable
- beurre Gaborit demi sel : negligeable
------
= Salting guidelines

calamar : no salt
crevettes : 0.5 tsp
1kg lamb : 1 tsp
200g cabillaud : 0.25+


maquereau : no salt
500g entrecote : 0.25 tsp salt
6 eggs : 0.125 tsp salt
steak haché with cheese : no salt


----------
= Example meals

500g entrecote + 60g beurre demi-sel + 0.25 tsp salt
    Sodium : 1160mg
    Potassium : 1825mg

5 steak haché 15% + 200g fromage
    Sodium : 1760mg
    Potassium : 1825mg
    
Total : 2920mg sodium
        3650mg potassium
To achieve 2.2:1 ratio
    I'm supplementing 3000mg potassium
